data.description: *ALL OFFERS DUE SUNDAY ARPIL 7TH AT 5PM*  Beautifully maintained, fully updated tri-level in a wonderful area of Woodhaven. Walk into a bright, welcoming living room with hardwood floors. Continue through to the open concept kitchen and dining room with newer cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The back patio is located just off the kitchen and is perfect for summer entertaining. Upstairs you will find three bedrooms and a lovely updated full bath. The fully finished lower level features a stylish half bath, and a spacious family room with new carpet that is perfect for movie nights. The sizable laundry room provides natural light through two large windows and offers plenty of space for storage. This home is situated on a large corner lot, and has an oversized 2 car garage perfect for a man cave, work shop, or car enthusiast. Welcome home!
